## Challenge Description

> A corrupted mobile backup is all that remains of a wiped conversation. Sort the real evidence from the noise, reconstruct what actually happened, and recover the hidden key.

We are given a backup export with two folders of interest:

- `app_export/` — real conversation artifacts (SQLite database, cached attachment chunks, metadata)
- `decoy/` — single `quarantine_note.txt` (misleading noise)

